---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="trampa"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-trap"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--narrow wheat-text-center">
        <div class="wheat-space-y-12">
            <div>
                <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-trap-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase">
                    La Trampa
                </span>
                <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-5xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-trap-title wheat-mt-4 wheat-mb-8">
                    El Regalo Envenenado
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-space-y-8 wheat-text-lg wheat-text-xl@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-trap-desc wheat-max-w-2xl wheat-mx-auto">
                <p>
                    Parecía un regalo: comida segura. Pero el trigo exigía un servicio constante.
                    Limpiar el campo, traer agua, espantar plagas.
                </p>
                <p class="wheat-font-bold wheat-trap-quote wheat-text-2xl wheat-text-3xl@md">
                    <ShareableQuote
                        quote="¿Domesticamos al trigo... o el trigo nos domesticó a nosotros?"
                    />
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-pt-12">
                <div class="wheat-trap-card wheat-p-6 wheat-p-8@md wheat-rounded wheat-border wheat-inline-block">
                    <p class="wheat-font-mono wheat-text-sm wheat-text-base@md wheat-trap-card-text wheat-italic">
                        &gt; "Este punto de unión sostiene todas las ciudades de la Tierra."
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-trap {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-trap-chapter {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-trap-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-trap-desc {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
    .wheat-trap-quote {
        color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.9);
    }
    .wheat-trap-card {
        background-color: #292524;
        border-color: rgba(146, 64, 14, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-trap-card-text {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-p-8\@md {
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .wheat-text-base\@md {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
    }
</style>
